---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="How Emerito handles the personal data you share with us."
  lang="en"
  alternateHref="/privacidad"
>
  <div class="pop-root relative w-full overflow-hidden">

    <section class="bg-cream pt-20 pb-14 px-6 lg:px-[46px] border-b-[3px] border-blue-black">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <p class="pop-badge text-xs px-3.5 py-1.5 bg-orange text-blue-black border-[2.5px] border-blue-black mb-6">Legal</p>
        <h1 class="font-display font-medium text-[clamp(38px,5vw,68px)] leading-[0.95] tracking-[-0.02em] text-blue-black mb-5">
          Privacy <em class="italic text-orange">policy.</em>
        </h1>
        <p class="font-mono text-xs text-blue-black/45 uppercase tracking-[0.08em]">Last updated: July 2026</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-cream py-16 px-6 lg:px-[46px]">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-10 text-[15.5px] leading-[1.65] text-blue-black/75">

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-blue-black mb-3">Who we are</h2>
          <p>
            Emerito is a creative content studio based in Medellín, Colombia. This site is
            <strong class="text-blue-black">emerito.co</strong>. For anything related to your
            personal data, write to us at
            <a href="mailto:miguel@emerito.co" class="font-bold text-orange underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-blue-black transition-colors">miguel@emerito.co</a>.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-blue-black mb-3">What we collect</h2>
          <p class="mb-3">
            <strong class="text-blue-black">Contact forms:</strong> your name, email address, and
            message, plus your organization and phone number if you choose to include them.
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong class="text-blue-black">Analytics &amp; cookies:</strong> we use measurement
            tools to understand how the site is used and how our content performs. These tools may
            set cookies and collect usage data such as pages visited, approximate location, device
            and browser information, and interactions with the site. Embedded content (such as
            YouTube videos) may also set its own cookies under the provider's policy.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-blue-black mb-3">The tools we use</h2>
          <ul class="space-y-2 mb-3">
            <li><strong class="text-blue-black">Google Tag Manager</strong> — loads and manages the tools below.</li>
            <li><strong class="text-blue-black">Google Analytics 4</strong> — anonymous usage statistics (pages, sessions, traffic sources).</li>
            <li><strong class="text-blue-black">Meta Pixel</strong> — measures the performance of our content and ads on Meta platforms.</li>
            <li><strong class="text-blue-black">Microsoft Clarity</strong> — anonymized session insights (heatmaps, scroll behavior) to improve usability.</li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            You can limit this tracking at any time: block cookies in your browser settings, use
            your browser's private mode, or install
            <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="font-bold text-orange underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-blue-black transition-colors">Google's opt-out add-on</a>.
            You can also manage ad preferences in your
            <a href="https://www.facebook.com/adpreferences" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="font-bold text-orange underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-blue-black transition-colors">Meta ad settings</a>.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-blue-black mb-3">What we use it for</h2>
          <p>
            Form data is used for one thing: responding to your inquiry. Your message is delivered
            to our inbox by <strong class="text-blue-black">Formspree</strong> (our form provider,
            acting as a data processor), and you receive an automatic confirmation. Analytics data
            is used to improve the site and our content. We don't sell your data or add you to any
            mailing list.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-blue-black mb-3">How long we keep it</h2>
          <p>
            Your message lives in our email inbox for as long as the conversation is relevant.
            You can ask us to delete it at any time.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-blue-black mb-3">Your rights</h2>
          <p>
            Under Colombia's Law 1581 of 2012 (habeas data) you may know, update, correct, and
            request deletion of your personal data, and revoke any authorization you've given us.
            To exercise any of these rights, email
            <a href="mailto:miguel@emerito.co" class="font-bold text-orange underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-blue-black transition-colors">miguel@emerito.co</a>
            and we'll respond within the legal terms.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

  </div>
</BaseLayout>
